{"lemma":"مَرْبِطِ","slug":"مَرْبِطِ","root":"ر.ب.ط","root_slug":"ر-ب-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ب-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14514","n14515"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%90%D8%B7%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place where you tie something","examples":[{"text":"مَرْبِط الْفَرَس","english":"the key thing"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place of the verb رَبَطَ (rabaṭa)."},"ipa":["/mar.batˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14514","headword_ar":"مَرْبِطٌ","root":"rbT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marobaTN","text_ar":"مَرْبَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S K,) the former used by him who says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arobuTu","text_ar":"اَرْبُطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the latter by him who says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arobuTu","text_ar":"اَرْبُطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IB,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where a beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is tied, bound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made fast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAbiTu","text_ar":"مَرَابِطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 33.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lahu marobiaTu EanozK","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لَهُ مَرْبَِطُ عَنْزٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not"},{"kind":"text","text":"so much as, or even,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place where a she-goat is tied"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) Each is a noun of place used in a definite manner; so that you may not say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa min~iY marobaTa Alfarasi","text_ar":"هُوَ مِنِّى مَرْبَطَ الفَرَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaATa Alv~uray~aA","text_ar":"مَنَاطَ الثُّرَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA: [in which, however, the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mnAT","text_ar":"مناط"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been inadvertently omitted.]) ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place where soldiers tie their horses at the frontier in preparation for the enemy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where they keep post on the frontier;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraAbaTN","text_ar":"مُرَابَطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". You say,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlguzaApu fiY maraAbiTihimo","text_ar":"الغُزَاةُ فِى مَرَابِطِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraAbaTaAtihimo","text_ar":"مُرَابَطَاتِهِمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The warriors are in their places where they tie their horses at the frontier in preparation for the enemy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where they keep post on the frontier."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","IB"]},{"entry_id":"n14515","headword_ar":"مِرْبَطٌ","root":"rbT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaATN","text_ar":"رِبَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}